Template: chaos/ask_mds
Type: Boolean
Default: false
Description: Do you want to setup a MDS node?
	     This will setup a MDS server (need to know persistent DB MONGO servers).

Template: chaos/ask_cds
Type: Boolean
Default: false
Description: Do you want to setup a CDS node?
	     This will setup a CDS server (need to know persistent DB MONGO servers and MDS).

Template: chaos/ask_webui
Type: Boolean
Default: false
Description: Do you want to setup a WEBUI node?
	     This will setup a CHAOS WEB server (need to know a MDS server).

Template: chaos/ask_wan
Type: Boolean
Default: false
Description: Do you want to setup a WAN node?
	     This will setup a WAN server (need to know a MDS server).

Template: chaos/ask_us
Type: Boolean
Default: false
Description: Do you want to setup a Chaos Unit Server node?
	     This will setup a CHAOS Unit Server (need to know a MDS server).

Template: chaos/ask_mongo
Type: String
Default: localhost
Description: Specify a comma separated lists of mongo servers
	     This will setup the mongo backend.

Template: chaos/ask_couchbase
Type: String
Default: localhost
Description: Specify a comma separated lists of couchbase servers
	     This will setup the couchbase backend.

Template: chaos/ask_dbuser
Type: String
Default: chaos
Description: Specify the DB user
	     This will setup the DB username.

Template: chaos/ask_dbpass
Type: Password
Default: chaos
Description: Specify the DB password
	     This will setup the DB password.

Template: chaos/ask_mdsurl
Type: String
Default: localhost:5000
Description: Specify the MDS url (ip:port)
	     This will setup the MDS server.

Template: chaos/ask_usalias
Type: String
Description: Specify the Unit Server UID
	     This will setup an UnitServer with the specified UID.

Template: chaos/ask_mdstest
Type: Boolean
Default: true
Description: Do you want to initialize MDS with a TEST configuration?
	     This will setup a MDS TEST configuration.